          "title": "Attempt to prove zerika moment from ha'pigul l'olam moalin bo braisa",
          "display_title": "L'olam proof",
          "timestamp": "50:00"
        },
        {
          "title": "Gemara initially infers from l'olam that pigul at early stage is problem",
          "display_title": "L'olam early",
          "timestamp": "50:31"
        },
        {
          "title": "Answer: no, zerika was done with pigul; l'olam emphasizes pigul always problematic",
          "display_title": "Zerika pigul",
          "timestamp": "51:00"
        },
        {
          "title": "Rashi interpretation and questions about the derivation of timing from braisa",
          "display_title": "Rashi interpret",
          "timestamp": "51:29"
        },
        {
          "title": "Gemara resolves: l'olam underscores Rav Gidal's principle, emphasis on zerika moment",
          "display_title": "Rav Gidal zerika",
